    <item>
      <title>银行强烈反对后欧洲央行将推迟公布杠杆贷款调查结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ecb-is-set-to-delay-findings-of-leveraged-loans-probe-after-backlash-from-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将推迟公布针对高风险贷款的大规模调查结果，这意味着该行默认其认为多家银行对该调查的投诉是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ecb-is-set-to-delay-findings-of-leveraged-loans-probe-after-backlash-from-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cerberus 正在洽谈从 Hoist 收购 20 亿欧元西班牙贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cerberus-in-talks-to-buy-2-billion-spanish-portfolio-from-hoist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Cerberus Capital Management LP 是从 Hoist Finance AB 收购价值逾 20 亿欧元（22 亿美元）西班牙不良贷款组合的领先者之一。]]></description>
